Package org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.core.jmx.mbean

This package contains all accounting related classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AllAccountsMBean
    MBean interface for viewing an account of the ProActive Resource Manager.
    ManagementMBean
    MBean interface for the management of the Resource Manager.
    MyAccountMBean
    MBean interface representing the attributes of an account.
    RuntimeDataMBean
    This MBean interface exposes runtime Resource Manager statistics:
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllAccountsMBeanImpl
    Implementation of the AllAccountsMBean interface.
    ManagementMBeanImpl
    Implementation of the ManagementMBean interface.
    MyAccountMBeanImpl
    Implementation of the MyAccountMBean interface.
    RuntimeDataMBeanImpl
    This class implements RuntimeDataMBean to expose the runtime data of the Resource Manager following the JMX standard for management.

Package org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.core.jmx.mbean Description

This package contains all accounting related classes.
